word: das Wurstwar, die There is no plural form for the singular noun "wurstwar" as it seems to be a misspelling or a non-existent word.
definition: A type of food product typically made from ground meat, spices, and other ingredients, often encased in a cylindrical shape. It is commonly consumed as a main course or used as an ingredient in various dishes.
